reviewText: Jamie is the most annoying actor Ive ever seen, But bonanza is my favorite series next to gunsmoke, love Loren  Green and the whole cast, even in his more mild mannered older age, still comes off as a strong will,  patriarch, I guess all things run their course ,I just wish they would have spared this great series such a whiny little brat, as I watch these old episodes this kid just gets under my skin royally, have fun watching friends
